Meta

property value
dataset name Building Permits
data source City of Chicago
data level City
description Permits issued by the Department of Buildings in the City of Chicago from 2006 to the present. The dataset for each year contains more than 65,000 records/rows of data and cannot be viewed in full in Microsoft Excel. Therefore, when downloading the file, select CSV from the Export menu. Open the file in an ASCII text editor, such as Wordpad, to view and search. Data fields requiring description are detailed below.
permalink https://data.cityofchicago.org/Buildings/Building-Permits/ydr8-5enu
dataset key ydr8-5enu
number of records 419250
number of variables 143
